Dive deep into the world of fairytales, discover classical works, absorb the atmosphere of horror, listen to the Brothers Grimm’s fairy tales in German! And now you can even read the subtitles for the book you are listening to due to the power of Artificial Intelligence!


Check out the works of famous writers such as Bierce, Chekhov, Van Dyke, and many others:

- Subtitles for the book you are listening to
